     <p>
      <img alt="" height="144" src="/images/bfs_main_body.jpg" width="700"/>
     </p>
     <h2>
      Welcome to Business and Financial Services
     </h2>
     <p>
      As part of the
      <a href="http://bas.ucr.edu" target="_blank">
       Business &amp; Administrative Services
      </a>
      organization, the mission of Business and Financial Services is to support research, instruction, and public service by providing prompt, reliable business and financial information and services while balancing compliance with applicable laws, regulations, and policies.
     </p>
     <p>
      Business and Financial Services includes Accounting, Business Contracts, Equipment Management, Procurement Services, and Student Business Services (SBS) / Cashiers.
     </p>
     <p>
      In the future, this site will host most pages for departments of Business and Financial Services, but for now, please follow the links below for relevant information:
     </p>
     <ul>
      <li>
       <p>
        <a href="http://accounting.ucr.edu" target="_blank">
         Accounting
        </a>
       </p>
      </li>
      <li>
       <p>
        <a href="http://procurement.ucr.edu/contracts/">
         Business Contracts
        </a>
       </p>
      </li>
      <li>
       <p>
        <a href="/equipment/">
         Equipment Management
        </a>
       </p>
      </li>
      <li>
       <p>
        <a href="http://procurement.ucr.edu/procurement/">
         Procurement Services (Purchasing)
        </a>
       </p>
      </li>
      <li>
       <p>
        <a href="http://www.sbs.ucr.edu/">
         Student Business Services / Cashiers
        </a>
       </p>
      </li>
     </ul>
     <p>
      This web site was developed as a resource for the campus to easily access relevant policies, procedures, and other important financial services information.
     </p>
     <p>
      Sincerely,
     </p>
     <p>
      <strong>
       Bobbi McCracken
      </strong>
      <br/>
      Associate Vice Chancellor - Business and Financial Services &amp; Controller
     </p>
     <p style="text-align: left;">
      <a href="/bfs-org-chart.pdf" target="_blank">
       BFS Organization Chart
      </a>
      (December 2018)
     </p>
    </div>
